# Khet-Set-Go — Crop Disease Detection System (CRPDS)

AI-powered crop disease detection for Rice, Wheat, and Sugarcane, built for smallholder farmers with zero recurring cost.

---

## The Problem

Standard detection tools fail in real-world farm conditions because:

- They analyze irrelevant background data — soil, shadows, weeds — instead of the plant
- Basic CNNs process noisy data, leading to high misdiagnosis rates
- Existing mobile apps lack the computational depth for reliable, high-precision detection

---

## The Solution

CRPDS uses a surgical masking and hybrid cloud pipeline approach:

1. **SAM (Segment Anything Model)** isolates the infected leaf from all background noise
2. A **CNN classifier** runs on the clean masked image for accurate disease identification
3. A **FastAPI backend** hosted on Google Colab and tunnelled via **ngrok** handles inference, bringing professional-grade AI to any standard Android phone

---

## Process Flow

```
CAPTURE  ->  SEGMENT  ->  CLASSIFY  ->  RESULT

Camera input    SAM isolates     CNN identifies     Confidence score
on-device       crop region      disease class      + AI feedback
```

---

## Supported Crops and Diseases

**Wheat**
- Yellow Rust
- Brown Rust
- Healthy

**Rice**
- Bacterial Blight
- Blast
- Brown Spot

**Sugarcane**
- Red Rot
- Rust
- Mosaic

---

## Tech Stack

- Mobile App: Android Studio
- Segmentation: SAM (Segment Anything Model)
- Classification: CNN (Convolutional Neural Network)
- Backend: FastAPI
- Tunnel: ngrok
- Runtime: Google Colab
- Dataset: Kaggle + Custom Dataset

---

## Results

*Wheat* — Yellow Rust, Brown Rust, Healthy
Accuracy: 98%

*Rice* — Bacterial Blight, Blast, Brown Spot
Accuracy: 95%

*Sugarcane* — Red Rot, Rust, Mosaic
Accuracy: 97%

## Architecture Overview

```
Android App
    |
    v
Capture Image
    |
    v
SAM — Segment and Mask Leaf
    |
    v
FastAPI Backend via ngrok
    |
    v
CNN on Google Colab — Disease Classification
    |
    v
Confidence Score + AI Feedback displayed on App
```

---

## Why CRPDS Over Alternatives

**Background Isolation**
- Cloud Apps: No
- Basic CNN: No
- CRPDS: Yes

**Real-time Inference**
- Cloud Apps: Yes
- Basic CNN: Yes
- CRPDS: Yes

**Low-resource Device Support**
- Cloud Apps: No
- Basic CNN: Partial
- CRPDS: Yes

**Multi-disease Classification**
- Cloud Apps: Yes
- Basic CNN: Partial
- CRPDS: Yes

